The paper also heavily utilizes deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of attention layers, which are commonly used in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
